\" />"},{"pid":"ce663b17046f7d6b1dc94f59238a7424d3612e0a","tid":500812,"uid":38391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁雷切定千鳥勁啲？</blockquote><br />\n紫電勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b8a39b3b4534d7c0ada4f684a367c756888604","tid":500812,"uid":79442,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>穿透無撚敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班係漫畫有講過死門夜凱 勁到空間都扭曲埋"},{"pid":"6d06c38a56cc241fe109f15e9fc93041882d6072","tid":500812,"uid":31323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁雷切定千鳥勁啲？</blockquote><br />\nShow Blocked User - 山姆大叔.<br />\n究竟仲要block幾多個"},{"pid":"a2b6a3c5bd8a080553a70dbb5b33c5af1e04ed61","tid":500812,"uid":4173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:17:05.000Z","msg":"凱無得輸，最壞情況都係殺完你再自己死"},{"pid":"ac472b44e7ed59415cd459e5addcd96ad9f16c62","tid":500812,"uid":3914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:17:26.000Z","msg":"凱開八門要時間將查克拉灌入死門<br />\n卡卡西果下神威就完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3293cecc1c1d09b2d8c8a21359d2b3cfa3222da6","tid":500812,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"保守估計<br />\n卡卡西未反應到就夠佢死十次左右"},{"pid":"62ad2d9853124242dd4c83afee9479f6b8eec258","tid":500812,"uid":4683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T18:22:54.000Z","msg":"以我理解<br />\n如果雙眼卡卡西既話<br />\n一隻眼就係遠距離望到既野就可以吸入異空間<br />\n另一隻眼就係將自己成個或部分身體轉移到異空間<br />\n同埋近身捉住人同樣都吸到入異空間（呢招係帶土用既）<br />\n假設佢雙眼神威 理論上佢用到既只會係兩種能力<br />\n唔需要帶土單眼吸人果種能力<br />\n<br />\n而佢將自己身體轉移到異空間基本上係可以長開<br />\n睇返卡卡西對帶土神威既講解 同水門打帶土既了解係 只要攻擊 就要實體化 即係冇得轉移自己去異空間到 <br />\n<br />\n但同八門凱打 佢長開住神威 基本上佢唔需要發動攻擊 佢成個人已經轉移到異空間<br />\n<br />\n咁仲有咩討論價值？"},{"pid":"e89e3e6c276d520d33b79b1b69bfbc66d6a1bad3","tid":500812,"uid":44391,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b29db31ab9a44dc68d97a73900d5bb86c5e6cb7","tid":500812,"uid":49275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如討論下得番一隻腳既凱（倒立）夠唔夠冇眼卡卡西打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新思路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ceb049c1f1f5696d896205e692abfc535162c0a","tid":500812,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如討論下得番一隻腳既凱（倒立）夠唔夠冇眼卡卡西打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新思路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凱可以一隻手倒立，另一隻手出晝虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af84178cd2811a43bfe36428db5838c71919a79","tid":500812,"uid":101550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"打條撚咩<br />\n一見到你隻手督自己心口想開八門果下<br />\n即刻用神威入異空間<br />\n反正八門開左就一定要用<br />\n打唔打都計緊時<br />\n係異空間hea下訓下睇下書<br />\n本親熱天堂未睇完凱都已經死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6549a0098cb9c87aacfbe518ed4b301b71b4c4fd","tid":500812,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如討論下得番一隻腳既凱（倒立）夠唔夠冇眼卡卡西打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新思路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凱可以一隻手倒立，另一隻手出晝虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n倒立<br />\n切左隻腳叫網手幫佢移植初代細胞生返隻新嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf790